        Use roles system with Django
        
        Quickstart
        ----------
        
        Install django-exo-role::
        
            pip install django-exo-role
        
        Add it to your `INSTALLED_APPS`:
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            INSTALLED_APPS = (
                ...
                'exo_role',
                ...
            )
        
        Running Tests
        -------------
        
        Does the code actually work?
        
        ::
        
            source <YOURVIRTUALENV>/bin/activate
            (myenv) $ pip install tox
            (myenv) $ tox
        
